            <h2>Getting a Tax ID</h2>
            <p>If you wish to buy from OceanTailer, you will have to provide us with your Tax ID also called FEIN. We are not going to charge you any tax on the products our suppliers ship to you or to your customers.
                At the end of the year, we have to show the IRS why we did NOT charge you that tax.<br>
