            <h2>Do I need a Tax ID to work with you if I'm outside the US?</h2>
            <p>At the moment, we only work with USA Based retail companies. However, depends on the situation, we may work with international retailers. Please contact us for more information.
            </p><br>
            <h2>Can I use my website as my registered business name?</h2>
            <p>Your website or online store is your store name. Business names can differ from your store name. But the important thing is to register with your state. </p>
